ds_id: Meta to introduce parent-managed Meta Quest accounts@Telecompaper@2023-06-19 22:42:09.715917@Meta
data_content: Unfortunately, due to the ongoing pandemic, the company has decided to cancel their annual holiday party. While it is disappointing, the safety of their employees is their top concern and they do not want to risk anyone getting sick. They plan on finding alternative ways to show their appreciation and gratitude to their team.
